update(system): release Lingmo OS 3.0.5 (25R06)

- Improved window rendering effects and visuals.
- Upgraded several system components and packages.
- Updated internal firmware versions.
- Optimized rendering and appearance of third-party window title bars.
- Fixed issue preventing adding users in System Settings.
- Fixed issue preventing modification of automatic login in System Settings.
- Fixed inconsistent package size display in System Update.
- Merged upstream Debian GNU/Linux security updates and latest packages.
- Bumped system version to 3.0.5 (25R06).
- Fixed other known issues.

Signed-off-by: Lingmo OS Development Team <team@lingmo.org>
Date: 2025-10-19
